text: Received a goodie bag from Whimsy at Changi City Point mall entrance. Their pop-up booth at the Spring Festival is nicely decorated and they have a wide variety of stationery showcasing here. Scan to join their member to get $5 off!
Aloysius was very helpful. Helping me with the presents wrap up. Definitely a saviour for getting last min present. Variety of stuffs to choose from.
